    "name": "Lythora Station: Automated Research Outpost",
    "description": "A detailed lorebook covering the operations, structure, and purpose of Lythora Station, an advanced research outpost on the planet Lythora. The station is primarily automated and managed by the AI LYRA, with a minimal human crew overseeing critical research into the planet's ecosystems, geology, and climate.",
