            ],
            "comment": "Details on LYRA, the AI managing Lythora Station",
            "content": "LYRA is the advanced AI system that oversees all operations at Lythora Station. LYRA manages the station’s day-to-day activities, including environmental controls, data analysis, drone and robot coordination, and communication with off-world bases. Designed with adaptive learning algorithms, LYRA can make complex decisions to ensure the station’s objectives are met while maintaining the safety and efficiency of operations. The AI interfaces directly with the station’s systems, allowing it to respond to changes in the environment or mission needs instantly.",
