            "comment": "Focuses on the layout and purpose of the Central Hub",
            "content": "The Central Hub is the core of Lythora Station, housing the Command Center where LYRA, the operational AI, controls the station’s functions. The hub includes several specialized labs, a data processing core, and the station’s communication arrays. The Observation Deck, part of the Central Hub, provides panoramic views of Lythora’s diverse landscapes, serving as both a research area and a place for the crew to gather.",
